body_html: When can we expect the official build of TF 1.4.0 for Python 3.6? The official docs reference https://storage.googleapis.com/tensorflow/linux/gpu/tensorflow_gpu-1.4.0-cp36-cp36m-linux_x86_64.whl as the Python 3.6 version, but I am still getting the original warning.
